net.wimpi.modbus.msg

Class MaskWriteRegisterResponse

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.wimpi.modbus.msg.ModbusMessageImpl
      • net.wimpi.modbus.msg.ModbusResponse
        • net.wimpi.modbus.msg.MaskWriteRegisterResponse
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Transportable, ModbusMessage

    public final class MaskWriteRegisterResponse
extends ModbusResponse
    Class implementing a MaskWriteRegisterResponse. The implementation directly correlates with the class 0 function write single register (FC 6). It encapsulates the corresponding response message.
    Version:
    1.2rc1 (09/11/2004)
    Author:
    Dieter Wimberger
